name: Tear in space time
description: A circle of human surrounds a tear , reversing the decisions and actions. white layer shows their memories fading away. They lost all their experience. Mistakes are good. Sometimes they are bad and we can't learn from them. We sometimes have to go back in time and change that.I used ink to create a skin-like texture. The ink creates a soft plastic finish. The acrylic do not mix with the soft ink finish. It simple covers it.
